data.description: Sellers states "Bring all reasonable offers!!!" If you appreciate the vintage aesthetic, you absolutely must take a look at this meticulously maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located on the north side of Temple. Situated on a corner lot, this charming residence is adorned with beautiful native trees that offer ample shade during the scorching summer months. Step inside and be amazed by the generous amount of space, perfect for creating multiple dining areas and versatile living arrangements. The rooms are impressively spacious, and the storage capacity in this house is truly remarkable considering its age. Without a doubt, this home deserves a prominent spot on your must-see list!
